snippet: With the recent demonstration of a drone-based delivery system by Google, the tech industry’s enthusiasm for the devices seems undimmed — but some issues will be difficult to solve.
abstract: Google's demonstration of Project Wing, drone delivery system, shows that tech industry's enthusiasm for drones continues undimmed, but plenty of issues with delivery-by-drone services have yet to be resolved.
lead_paragraph: With the recent demonstration of a drone-based delivery system by Google, the tech industry’s enthusiasm for the devices seems undimmed — but some issues will be difficult to solve.

headline.main: Drone Developers Consider Obstacles That Cannot Be Flown Around
headline.print_headline: Drone Developers Consider Obstacles That Cannot Be Flown Around
